{"type": "article", "id": 8540, "title": "Policosmos 家族儿童玩具", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-16T07:42:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235058O5TrbDftEk2CHyP7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t西班牙设计工作室 PCM 带来了一套 Policosmos 家族儿童玩具，这个家族由来自热带和寒带的八个小动物组成，小动物有着简单的外形和安全的材质，适用于多个年龄段的小朋友。此外，PCM 为他们创造了各种各样的场景，以此来激发孩子们的想像力和讲故事的欲望。这是 <a href=\"http://www.pcmdesign.es/\" target=\"_blank\">PCM 的官方主页</a>，课业查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235056kUfNT47FXe0V1xbQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235057HWNwMV2j5zbt0SXm.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235057iWR7tuO3NI1C9oxY.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235057Ig6XDOp4jemwda2q.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}